    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> The most troubling bug was my \"Attempt 3\", where it just threw an error when to change the reset template. Do any of your changes address this?\r\n\r\nIndeed. There is an open PR for that https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/pull/2585\r\n\r\n>  > use the root css class for configuring the containers\r\n\r\n> Would this make my above Attempt 1 and Attempt 2 _both_ work?\r\n\r\nYes. It would have removed the friction. The root class is used inside a template, which gets removed when using a custom template.",
